{
  "texts": [
    "Furthermore, it gives more reliable features compared to various feature extraction approaches.",
    "For HOG extraction of features, 64 × 128-pixel images are pre-processed.",
    "This is achievable with 8 × 8 and 16 × 16 image patches, respectively.",
    "After that, the gradient is estimated for every pixel in both the x and y directions.",
    "The value of each pixel in each region can be determined more accurately with the assistance of a gradient approach."
  ]
}